Mahathir bin Mohamad
[[Image:Mahathir bin Mohamad.jpg|thumb|Mahathir bin Mohamad, the Malaysian Allah]]
[[File:Mahathirfun.jpg|thumb|Mahathir enjoys fun nights out in [[Texas|gay bondage clubs]].]]
'''Mahathir bin Mohamad''' (being a [[Moonspeak|foreign name]], probably not pronounced the way it's spelt) is the former Prime Minister of [[Malaysia]], who assumed power in the [[1980s]], and stayed there until recently. An [[Islam|Islamic]] megalomaniac, he spent his time in office telling such truths as how the [[JEWS DID WTC|Jews destroyed the World Trade Center]], [[homosexuals]] are the cause of all the worlds problems, and [[bullshit|how great Malaysia is]]. He also invested much effort into a [[War on drugs]] and a War on homosexuality, while not even bothering with such trivial victimless crimes as [[Murder]], [[Rape]], or [[child abuse]].

Outside of politics, his hobbies include being [[Asian]], worshiping [[Allah]], pretending to be Allah, abusing human rights, and yelling about how Western Countries abuse human rights. He currently has his own [[Weblog|blog]], filled with his [[Shit nobody cares about|acclaimed views on the world]] and a rare picture of him smiling. He also has seven children whose names all start with M, who he sold into [[slavery]].

Within Malaysia, he is often worshiped as though he is Allah. This is done in secret, as they are scared that if Allah finds out, he will end the world. This is just [[insane]], however, seeing as Allah's not real like [[Jesus]], so what they really should be afraid of is going to hell for being heathens when they die.

==About==
Mahathir bin Mohamad was probably born in Malaysia, based on him being Malaysian and all. He's also a doctor apparently, but he's Asian so it would only be notable if he wasn't. As a child he was continuously raped by gay Rabbi's, which lead to his lifelong hatred of Jews and fags. Despite this, one of his closest allies was a closet homosexual named Anwar Ibrahim. Mohamad was outraged to learn of Anwar's gayness, especially as this revelation meant all the [[sex]] they had been having was therefore [[gay sex]]. Anwar ended up going to [[prison]] for nine years as a result.

After retiring from politics, he has become a professional [[Internet Tough Guy|keyboard warrior]], ranting about how shit he thinks everyone who succeeded him is. These ventures were interrupted by numerous heart attacks, which were (he claims), brought on by Jews and [[Americans]]. Unfortunately, he recovered fully from these.

==Relationship with other World leaders==
[[Image:HowardFinger.jpg|thumb|Every meeting between Mohamad and [[United States of Australia|Australian]] PM [[John Howard]] consisted solely of this]]

Mohamad was butt hurt by many other world leaders, due to their endorsement of completely fair and reasonable policies, which went against Mohamad's plans for world domination, and the [[holocaust|elimination of fags and Jews]]. He also had an intense fear of [[White people]], which made negotiations with places like America and Australia hard. He combated his fear by insulting them, but this was [[before the internet]], so was unable to do so behind the safety of a computer screen. This resulted in his insults being printed in newspapers [[stupid]] enough to listen to him. Despite his issues with those countries, Mohamad has a constant hard on for [[China]], and often dreamed of physically being one of the tanks at Tienanmen Square. The fact that his dream never came true lead to serious depression, which he combated by killing [[children]].

